# CMake and vcpkg (Cursor rule)

- Presets must inherit `normalized-build-environment` (see `tools/check-toolchain.ps1` and `AGENTS.md`).
- Install optional packages only via `pwsh -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File tools/bootstrap-deps.ps1`. CMake configure stays on `VCPKG_MANIFEST_INSTALL=OFF` and `VCPKG_INSTALLED_DIR=${sourceDir}/vcpkg_installed`.
- Do not delete `external/vcpkg`; restore with `git clone https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg.git external/vcpkg` then bootstrap when missing.
- **`MK_tools`:** cluster `OBJECT` targets under `engine/tools/{shader,gltf,asset,scene}/`; see [`docs/specs/2026-05-11-directory-layout-target-v1.md`](../../docs/specs/2026-05-11-directory-layout-target-v1.md).
